A personal attempt to create a web project that includes a frontpage,
a blog and some more cool stuff. It's written in Python and by using
django framework.


REQUIREMENTS
----------------

* django (>= 1.3)
* django-tagging
* python-imaging
* BeautifulSoup (optional when using colorizing)
* python-south
* django-markitup
* python2-markdown


NOTES ON DEPLOYMENT
-----------------------

* you can overwrite any setting by creating settings in local_settings.py
(you need to create it first)
* /favicon.ico should be defined in web server configuration file as an alias
to /static/images/favicon.png
